Standards-Version: 4.6.0
Homepage: https://github.com/nikaakin/alarm-notify
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: alarm-notify
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, bash, libnotify-bin, alsa-utils
Description: Simple timer notifications with sound and custom messages
 A shell script that sets a countdown timer and shows a desktop
 notification with optional sound when time is up. Supports running
 in external terminal windows or silently in the background.
